  "title": "Namespace Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Outputs",
  "content": "<h1 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Outputs' data-commentId='N:Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Outputs' id='Alis_Core_Aspect_Logging_Outputs'>Namespace Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Outputs   </h1>\r\n <h3 class='section'>Classes</h3><dl class='parameters'><dt> <a href='Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Outputs.AsyncLogOutput.html'>AsyncLogOutput</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Outputs.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Wraps an output and queues writes to process them asynchronously.\nUseful for file and network I/O to avoid blocking the main thread.\nAOT-compatible: Uses queuing and thread management, no reflection.</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt> <a href='Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Outputs.ConsoleLogOutput.html'>ConsoleLogOutput</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Outputs.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Writes log entries to the standard console output.\nUses colored output when available based on log level.\nThread-safe: Console.WriteLine is thread-safe in .NET.\nAOT-compatible: No reflection, simple console I/O.</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt> <a href='Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Outputs.DebugLogOutput.html'>DebugLogOutput</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Outputs.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Writes log entries to the debugger output (Debug.WriteLine).\nOnly writes output when debugger is attached.\nUseful for development-time debugging.\nAOT-compatible: Uses Debug.WriteLine, no reflection.</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt> <a href='Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Outputs.FileLogOutput.html'>FileLogOutput</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Outputs.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Writes log entries to a file on disk.\nSupports appending to existing files and creates directories as needed.\nThread-safe: Uses a lock for file writes.\nAOT-compatible: Uses standard file I/O, no reflection.</p>\n\r\n</dd><dt> <a href='Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Outputs.MemoryLogOutput.html'>MemoryLogOutput</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Aspect.Logging.Outputs.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Stores log entries in memory for inspection and debugging.\nUseful for testing and retrieving recent log entries.\nThread-safe: Uses locks for access to the entries list.\nAOT-compatible: No reflection, pure collection-based storage.</p>\n\r\n</dd></dl>",
